subSubSection.paragraph:
Geographical distribution. Antilles, Colombia and Brazil (
Hendler et al . 1995
). In Brazil , the species was recorded from Rio Grande do Norte to Bahia ( Tommasi 1969 ; present study). The bathymetric distribution is down to 60 m deep ( Martínez 1991 ). Here, the specimens were found only in the intertidal zone.
